aces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有心點會搵唔到，大把人打針吸毒</blockquote><br />\n有啲藥房其實有賣,睇佢肯唔肯賣比你<br />\n不過印象打空氣要打大量先死得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">買過針筒拆針頭餵小動物食藥</span>"},{"pid":"62af0c43793e70443d4777d3255942c0b5905484","tid":370070,"uid":95494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T23:07:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016f71c9a258ccd834e985acf90c73b4e16f6ae3","tid":370070,"uid":42187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T23:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跳乜柒樓，都無啲知識<br />\n新聞都教吸氦氣無痛自殺啦</blockquote><br />\n有人話唔係無痛</blockquote><br />\n專家死撚左未？"},{"pid":"09c663e0c18c6daa2426875460bdbd35d1bb9fbd","tid":370070,"uid":118360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T23:22:14.000Z","msg":"樓主做乜想死"},{"pid":"79458de02632c5f6d94f51de35f3db93f3d39579","tid":370070,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T23:33:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7cb127b67658a71ed9965c7536dfd9f827fb56dd","tid":370070,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打空氣落血管死唔死得</blockquote><br />\n針筒咁難搵到...</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有心點會搵唔到，大把人打針吸毒</blockquote><br />\n有啲藥房其實有賣,睇佢肯唔肯賣比你<br />\n不過印象打空氣要打大量先死得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">買過針筒拆針頭餵小動物食藥</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n針筒通街都有啦<br />\n但打空氣入血自殺真係好少聽<br />\n要注意既係，如果氣泡上腦，你會中風但死唔去，到時半身不遂，麻煩到屋企人照顧，或要長住療養院，咁就真係生不如死"},{"pid":"d48d652f6f00d1d058cfef9634b811a84d375474","tid":370070,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:35:10.000Z","msg":"過量麻醉可一睡不醒"},{"pid":"aa98fa43cc6d71c5480d2f2e1f040c51a68763e9","tid":370070,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:40:14.000Z","msg":"痛到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e0d9c2d1825e1c9a0edd7049201b447d8b3689","tid":370070,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:42:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打空氣落血管死唔死得</blockquote><br />\n中風，但唔死得<br />\nfrom最近單新聞"},{"pid":"fbb2f3c0cfa1b106cf45505ed9bb3525df0ada12","tid":370070,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:43:17.000Z","msg":"F=ma <br />\n如果你70公斤就有700N 咁痛"},{"pid":"52f17156cea5d94d987e84331a8f2f32b6dc00ac","tid":370070,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T05:03:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽講半空就冇知覺<br />\n試左死左好痛唔好返黎搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>我聽過有個個案，跳樓落去唔死得，有知覺但郁唔到<br />\n<br />\n佢凌晨跳，無人發覺到，去到朝早8點有人番工先發現到佢，起碼痛左幾個鐘先送到入醫院<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好咁傻跳樓自殺</blockquote><br />\n仲有知覺架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係頭落地或傷重要器官咁個人咪未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892bfc481b0dbd6b90ceddb0aef83a169f9a453a","tid":370070,"uid":63648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T05:28:37.000Z","msg":"跳熱氣球好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b682605f9261bbc720fd5b0a4baa56c6814492","tid":370070,"uid":107217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T05:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>F=ma <br />\n如果你70公斤就有700N 咁痛</blockquote><br />\n咪拋書包啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要計N跳樓點都係Potential energy or kinetic去計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 況且痛都有單位架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9975500f0a0761b5c1e3bcd6ca342d2847e5f94","tid":370070,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T05:30:08.000Z","msg":"唔需要知 因為你唔會敢"},{"pid":"0a0ca1bbfb02c2dedfac562c8486d2c9bf12c8f7","tid":370070,"uid":131962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T05:39:52.000Z","msg":"跳樓感覺最快最一take過"},{"pid":"8b4aceafbf5d9bdc868843414d218d1969794566","tid":370070,"uid":104513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T06:34:29.000Z","msg":"痛唔痛 前題係你死未 未死痛成世 死就1秒都冇"}]}